# Basic bindings
## Apps
### browser
super + shift + Return
	$BROWSER
### dmenu
super + d
	dmenu_run
### copy-paste passwords
super + o
	dmenu-pass
### emoji input
super + p
	dmenu-emoji-input
### Terminal
super + Return
	$TERMINAL


## Lock
super + x
	i3lock

# Special Keys
## Brightness keys

XF86MonBrightnessDown
	xbacklight -dec 15
XF86MonBrightnessUp
	xbacklight -inc 15

## Media keys
XF86AudioMute
	amixer sset Master toggle
XF86Audio{Raise,Lower}Volume
	amixer sset Master 5%{+,-}
XF86Audio{Next,Prev}
	mpc {next,prev}
XF86AudioPlay
	mpc toggle
XF86Audio{Rewind,Forward}
	mpc seek {-,+}10
XF86Tools
	$TERMINAL -e ncmpcpp

## Caps lock
Caps_Lock
	pkill -RTMIN+10 i3blocks 
